{"tid":1767204,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實有兩樣野真係會害死人","createTime":"2019-12-03T06:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-13T05:33:29.000Z","uid":58335,"like":155,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"34d844ac619f8cc6cf80d353cb339ebeefda7ec7","tid":1767204,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:44:46.000Z","msg":"第一，瘋狂吹奏「今生只嫁/娶前線巴/絲」<br />\n<br />\n原意係冇咩問題<br />\n仲幾浪漫<br />\n但日子長左<br />\n浪漫主義害死人<br />\n<br />\n有啲人講講下就當真<br />\n見有部分人出去好似為識仔識女<br />\n打緊仗都可以𥄫仔/女<br />\n問拎電話都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你要嫁/娶自己知就得<br />\n唔建議瘋狂吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二，迫人勇武<br />\n每個人可以承受既後果都唔同<br />\n強制服兵役呀？<br />\n要進化自己識進化<br />\n你話同藍屍、中立撚分手就話，我都支持<br />\n但有啲話個男/女朋友係和理非<br />\n都話要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係男人一定要勇、女人就一定和理非<br />\n一方面又叫人尊重女人<br />\n另一方面又性別歧視和理非男<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山呀各位！！！"},{"pid":"b258ad172b9f462926cde589adb938d7630c38f5","tid":1767204,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfaf365034bac1dad385428a9c6ba18df02c7038","tid":1767204,"uid":327204,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"仲有啲on9 IG po自己啲gear出黎share 話又要起行。。 影自己隻手刮親有幾多滴血要報仇。。拎條爛褲po出黎問點解First aid要剪開佢。。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a694aed3c5bd1e14bc6654c7f743a89511b774d2","tid":1767